  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一张流程图，展示患者从社区到住院的完整路径，以及出院时遇到的瓶颈问题。核心是解释为什么急诊会拥堵——不是因为急诊本身，而是因为下游的\"出院阻滞\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "ED_Arrival",
        "Inpatient",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，您想表达的是\"访问阻滞\"（access block）机制——住院患者出不去，导致急诊患者进不来。起点是\"社区\"对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "access block mechanism"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，社区是起点。患者可以先找GP（全科医生），也可以直接去急诊。这两条路都要画出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把社区放在最左边，然后分出两条线：一条到GP，一条直接到急诊到达。GP那条线也连到急诊到达，这样逻辑就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来是急诊评估和治疗，然后有一个\"决策入院\"的节点，再到\"住院\"状态。这些是标准流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "\"决策入院\"这个节点，您希望突出它是一个关键决策点，还是作为普通过渡？我注意到后面要画阻滞，可能这个节点需要中性处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Admission"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "中性处理就好，用灰色。真正的重点是后面的\"准备出院\"以及两个阻滞节点：老年护理安置和NDIS支持。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我在\"住院\"后面加了\"准备出院\"，然后分出两个阻滞：一个是\"老年护理安置（容量限制）\"，另一个是\"NDIS支持/住宿（延迟/不匹配）\"。这两个我都用橙色虚线框标注为风险类。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "颜色方案上，我想区分几类：GP用浅蓝色（cth类），急诊治疗和住院用红色（state类），阻滞用橙色虚线（risk类），普通节点用灰色。这样视觉层次清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cth",
        "state",
        "risk",
        "neutral"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到。GP用#e1f5fe浅蓝，急诊治疗和住院用#ffebee红色，阻滞用#fff3e0橙色加6-4虚线，其他用#f5f5f5灰色。stroke颜色我也对应调整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "classDef cth",
        "classDef state",
        "classDef risk",
        "classDef neutral"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最关键的部分来了：要画两条反馈回路。第一条是\"占用率反馈回路\"——老年护理阻滞导致住院患者积压，直接反馈回住院节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "occupancy feedback loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这条反馈线是用虚线还是实线？我倾向用虚线，因为这不是正向流程，而是系统性的循环影响。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "同意，虚线。标注文字写\"occupancy feedback loop\"。第二条反馈更直接：高占用率限制急诊治疗能力，从住院连回急诊治疗。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inpatient",
        "ED_Treat",
        "high occupancy limits flow"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "两条虚线反馈都加上了。第一条：Block_Aged -.-|occupancy feedback loop| Inpatient；第二条：Inpatient -.-|high occupancy limits flow| ED_Treat。这样就把访问阻滞的机制可视化出来了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，NDIS阻滞Block_NDIS是不是也应该有类似的反馈？还是说它和老年护理阻滞共享同一条回路？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_NDIS",
        "Block_Aged"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "从机制上讲，Block_NDIS同样导致住院患者无法出院，占用床位，所以也应该连回Inpatient。不过如果您想简化，可以只保留一条代表性的反馈线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_NDIS",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "先保持现状吧，Block_Aged的反馈更具代表性，而且两条阻滞并列已经说明了问题多样性。NDIS的延迟性质稍有不同，不单独画反馈也可以。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我确认一下整体结构：Community → GP/ED_Arrival → ED_Treat → Admission → Inpatient → Ready → [Block_Aged | Block_NDIS]，加上两条反馈虚线。颜色类定义也全部应用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "flowchart LR",
        "classDef"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "字体用Inter吧，14px，线条颜色#444444。主题用base，这样样式控制更精确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "fontFamily",
        "fontSize",
        "lineColor",
        "theme"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已设置：theme为base，fontFamily为Inter, Arial, sans-serif，fontSize 14px，lineColor #444444。所有classDef的stroke-width统一2px，颜色对比度确保可读性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "init config",
        "classDef"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再看一眼：GP节点的标注是\"GP / primary care\"对吧？还有ED_Treat是\"ED assessment & treatment\"，这些长标注会不会换行有问题？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GP",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Mermaid会自动处理，不过我在Block_Aged和Block_NDIS里用了<br强制换行，比如\"Aged care placement<br(capacity constraint)\"，这样两行显示更紧凑。其他节点单行没问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美。这张图能清楚解释：为什么急诊拥堵不能只怪急诊——根源在社区护理和NDIS支持的系统性缺口。反馈回路把因果关系闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat",
        "access block mechanism",
        "feedback"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "最终检查完成：流程从左到右，四类颜色区分清晰，两条虚线反馈标注明确，所有节点和关系与您的临床逻辑一致。可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "flowchart LR",
        "Community",
        "Inpatient",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
